#. Tag: title
#: taskeditor.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Task Editor is used to create, edit, and delete tasks."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik nalog se uporablja za ustvarjanje, urejanje in brisanje nalog."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks can be organized into a hierarchical tree structure to any depth."
msgstr ""
"Naloge je mogoče organizirati v hierarhično drevesno strukturo do poljubne "
"globine."

#. Tag: title
#: taskeditor.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar provides the means to create, delete and move tasks and "
"milestones:"
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica ponuja sredstva za ustvarjanje, brisanje in premikanje nalog "
"in mejnikov:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: taskeditor.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button"
msgstr "Gumb"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: taskeditor.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Bližnjica"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: taskeditor.docbook:30 taskeditor.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Description</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Opis</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Task"
msgstr "Dodaj nalogo"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: taskeditor.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dropdown box to create a task or milestone. The new item is positioned after "
"the currently selected item on the same level as the selected item. If no "
"item is selected, the new item is appended at the top level."
msgstr ""
"Spustno polje za ustvarjanje naloge ali mejnika. Nov element je postavljen "
"za trenutno izbranim elementom na isti ravni kot izbrani element. Če ni "
"izbran noben element, se nov element doda na najvišjo raven."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:46 taskeditor.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: taskeditor.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Sub-task"
msgstr "Dodaj pod-nalogo"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: taskeditor.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dropdown box to create a sub-task or -milestone. The new item is appended as "
"a child to the currently selected item."
msgstr ""
"Spustno polje za ustvarjanje pod-naloge ali mejnika. Nov element je pripet "
"trenutno izbranemu elementu kot podrejeni element."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: taskeditor.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete Task"
msgstr "Izbriši nalogo"

#. Tag: keycap
#: taskeditor.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the selected tasks."
msgstr "Izbriše izbrano nalogo."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indent Task"
msgstr "Zamakni nalogo"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appends the selected task as a child to the task above."
msgstr "Doda izbrano nalogo kot podrejeno nalogi zgoraj."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unindent Task"
msgstr "Odzamakni nalogo"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moves the selected task one level up, inserting it after its current parent "
"task."
msgstr ""
"Premakne izbrano nalogo eno raven navzgor in jo vstavi za trenutno nadrejeno "
"nalogo."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Up"
msgstr "Pomakni navzgor"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves the selected task up one place."
msgstr "Premakne izbrano nalogo eno mesto navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Down"
msgstr "Premakni navzdol"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves the selected task down one place."
msgstr "Premakne izbrano nalogo za eno mesto navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you can also move or copy tasks using drag and drop or copy/paste."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko naloge premikate ali kopirate tudi z uporabo tehnike "
"povleci in spusti ali kopiraj/prilepi."

#. Tag: title
#: taskeditor.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Urejanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Data can be edited inline as described <link linkend=\"using-the-views"
"\">here</link> or by using the Task Settings Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Podatke je mogoče urejati neposredno, kot je opisano <link linkend=\"using-"
"the-views\">tukaj</link>, ali v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following columns are displayed as default:"
msgstr "Naslednji stolpci so privzeto prikazani:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: taskeditor.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column"
msgstr "Stolpec"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the task."
msgstr "Ime naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task status"
msgstr "Stanje naloge"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Responsible"
msgstr "Odgovorni"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "The person responsible for this task."
msgstr "Oseba odgovorna za to nalogo."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allocation"
msgstr "Dodelitev"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "List of resource allocations."
msgstr "Seznam dodeljenih virov."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "The type of task or the estimate type of the task."
msgstr "Vrsta naloge ali vrsta ocene naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The type can be set to <emphasis>Milestone</emphasis>, <emphasis>Effort</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>Duration</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Vrsto lahko nastavite na <emphasis>Mejnik</emphasis>, <emphasis>Napor</"
"emphasis> ali <emphasis>Trajanje</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Note:</guilabel> If the type is <emphasis>Summary</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>Project</emphasis> the type is not editable."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Opomba:</guilabel> Če je vrsta <emphasis>Povzetek</emphasis> ali "
"<emphasis>Projekt</emphasis>, vrste ni mogoče urejati."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Koledar"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The calendar used when estimate type is <emphasis>Duration</emphasis>."
msgstr "Koledar, uporabljen, ko je vrsta ocene <emphasis>Trajanje</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Estimate"
msgstr "Ocena"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most likely estimate. The estimate is the expected amount of effort or "
"time needed to complete a task. It can be expressed in different units: h "
"(hours), d (days), w (weeks) and M (months)."
msgstr ""
"Najverjetnejša ocena. Ocena je pričakovana količina napora ali časa, "
"potrebnega za dokončanje naloge. Lahko se izrazi v različnih enotah: h "
"(ure), d (dnevi), w (tedni) in M (meseci)."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Optimistic Ratio"
msgstr "Optimistično razmerje"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optimistic estimate expressed as a negative percentage of the most likely "
"estimate. (E.g. -20%)."
msgstr ""
"Optimistična ocena, izražena kot negativni odstotek najverjetnejše ocene. "
"(Npr. -20%)."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:210 taskeditor.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is only used if a PERT distribution is used."
msgstr "To se uporablja samo, če se uporablja distribucija PERT."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pessimistic Ratio"
msgstr "Pesimistično razmerje"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pessimistic estimate expressed as a positive percentage of the most likely "
"estimate. (E.g. 50%)."
msgstr ""
"Pesimistična ocena, izražena kot pozitiven odstotek najverjetnejše ocene. "
"(Npr. 50%)."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Risk"
msgstr "Tveganje"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Risk controls the PERT distribution used when calculating the actual "
"estimate for this task."
msgstr ""
"Tveganje nadzira porazdelitev PERT, ki se uporablja pri izračunu dejanske "
"ocene za to nalogo."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint"
msgstr "Omejitev"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "The timing constraint type."
msgstr "Vrsta časovne omejitve."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint Start"
msgstr "Začetek omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint start time."
msgstr "Začetni čas omejitve."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint End"
msgstr "Konec omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constraint end time."
msgstr "Končni čas omejitve."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running Account"
msgstr "Tekoči račun"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account for running costs."
msgstr "Račun za tekoče stroške."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup Account"
msgstr "Zagonski račun"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account for cost incurred at startup of the task."
msgstr "Račun za stroške, ki so nastali ob zagonu naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup Cost"
msgstr "Stroški zagona"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "The cost incurred at startup of the task."
msgstr "Stroški, ki nastanejo ob zagonu naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shutdown Account"
msgstr "Zapri račun"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account for cost incurred at shutdown of the task."
msgstr "Račun za stroške, ki so nastali ob zaustavitvi naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shutdown Cost"
msgstr "Stroški zaustavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "The cost incurred at shutdown of the task."
msgstr "Stroški, ki nastanejo ob zaustavitvi naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Description</para>"
msgstr "<para>Opis</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task notes."
msgstr "Opombe nalog."

#. Tag: title
#: taskeditor.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task Modules Docker"
msgstr "Sidrišče za module nalog"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task Modules are groups of tasks that can be reused across projects."
msgstr ""
"Moduli nalog so skupine nalog, ki jih je mogoče ponovno uporabiti v "
"projektih."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This makes it possible to draw on past experience and to standardize similar "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča črpanje iz preteklih izkušenj in standardizacijo podobnih "
"operacij."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A task module is inserted into your project by dragging it from the docker "
"and dropping it into your project."
msgstr ""
"Modul nalog se vstavi v vaš projekt tako, da ga povlečete iz okna in "
"spustite v svoj projekt."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A task module is a regular plan file, and is designed using &plan; in the "
"same way as designing a regular project."
msgstr ""
"Modul nalog je običajna datoteka načrta in je zasnovan z uporabo &plan; na "
"enak način kot načrtovanje običajnega projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A task module, however, typically includes only tasks, estimates, and "
"dependencies."
msgstr "Modul nalog pa običajno vključuje samo naloge, ocene in odvisnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The project name is displayed in the docker, and the description is used as "
"the tooltip."
msgstr ""
"Ime projekta je prikazano v priklopnem oknu, opis pa se uporablja kot opis "
"orodja."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A module can be opened for inspection or editing by double-clicking on the "
"module."
msgstr "Modul lahko odprete za pregled ali urejanje z dvojnim klikom na modul."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The modules can be grouped by storing them in different directories. Where "
"to search for them is configured using the Project Settings Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Module lahko združite tako, da jih shranite v različne imenike. Kje jih "
"iskati, je konfigurirano v pogovornem oknu za nastavitve projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Default values for new projects can be defined using the configuration "
"dialog, see <xref linkend=\"configure-plan-dialog\" xrefstyle=\"select:title"
"\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Privzete vrednosti za nove projekte je mogoče določiti s konfiguracijskim "
"pogovornim oknom, glejte <xref linkend=\"configure-plan-dialog\" xrefstyle="
"\"select:title\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: taskeditor.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resources Docker"
msgstr "Sidrišče virov"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Resources Docker offers a simple way to allocate resources to tasks by "
"selecting the resources you need and dragging them onto the "
"<emphasis>Allocation</emphasis> column."
msgstr ""
"Sidrišče virov ponuja preprost način dodeljevanja virov nalogam tako, da "
"izberete vire, ki jih potrebujete, in jih povlečete v stolpec "
"<emphasis>Dodelitev</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A resource can also be dropped on the <emphasis>Responsible</emphasis> "
"column."
msgstr "Vir lahko spustite tudi v stolpec <emphasis>Odgovorni</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: taskeditor.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allocations Docker"
msgstr "Sidrišče za dodelitve"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Allocations Docker displays the current resource allocation for the "
"selected task."
msgstr ""
"Sidrišče za dodelitve prikaže trenutno dodelitev sredstev za izbrano nalogo."

#. Tag: title
#: taskeditor.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the context menu, the view can be configured to show / hide the "
"Project, split / unsplit the tree view or it can be configured using the "
"configure dialog."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo kontekstnega menija lahko pogled konfigurirate za prikaz/skrivanje "
"projekta, razdelitev/razdelitev drevesnega pogleda ali pa ga lahko "
"konfigurirate z uporabo pogovornega okna za konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: para
#: taskeditor.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configure dialog enables you to tailor the amount of information the "
"view displays to fit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da količino informacij, ki jih "
"prikaže pogled, prilagodite svojim potrebam."
